1
00:00:43,502 --> 00:00:46,338
<i>After everything we've seen,</i>

2
00:00:46,505 --> 00:00:49,800
<i>there isn't much that rattles
either of us anymore.</i>

3
00:00:52,303 --> 00:00:54,180
<i>But this one...</i>

4
00:00:55,222 --> 00:00:57,475
<i>This one still haunts me.</i>

5
00:01:12,323 --> 00:01:14,158
<i>Two months prior to our involvement,</i>

6
00:01:14,325 --> 00:01:17,536
<i>the Lutz family had fled their home
in the middle of the night,</i>

7
00:01:17,703 --> 00:01:20,414
<i>claiming that the house was haunted.</i>

8
00:01:23,334 --> 00:01:26,170
<i>The Church had reached out to us for help.</i>

9
00:01:26,587 --> 00:01:27,797
<i>They wanted to see</i>

10
00:01:27,963 --> 00:01:31,592
<i>if we could confirm the activity
that had been reported by the Lutzes.</i>

11
00:01:32,593 --> 00:01:34,512
Mm-hmm.

12
00:01:35,304 --> 00:01:37,306
Okay. We ready?

13
00:01:38,474 --> 00:01:40,226
Then let's get started.

14
00:01:50,444 --> 00:01:53,072
I'd like you to sit quietly
and close your eyes.

15
00:01:56,659 --> 00:01:59,203
Envision yourself in a halo
of glowing white light.

16
00:02:00,329 --> 00:02:02,331
It will protect you.

17
00:02:04,625 --> 00:02:06,627
<i>The year before
the Lutzes moved in,</i>

18
