19
00:02:08,963 --> 00:02:12,299
<i>had brutally murdered his
entire family in this house.</i>

20
00:02:13,134 --> 00:02:14,468
<i>We'd hoped to discover</i>

21
00:02:14,635 --> 00:02:17,680
<i>if the killings had been
motivated purely by anger</i>

22
00:02:17,847 --> 00:02:19,223
<i>or if,</i>

23
00:02:19,390 --> 00:02:21,725
<i>as Ronny DeFeo testified in court,</i>

24
00:02:21,892 --> 00:02:26,021
<i>he had been under the influence
of something demonic.</i>

25
00:03:05,186 --> 00:03:08,898
<i>Stay here. Stay.</i>

26
00:03:33,464 --> 00:03:36,217
<i>Kill her. Kill her.</i>

27
00:03:38,302 --> 00:03:39,887
<i>Shoot them.</i>

28
00:03:40,054 --> 00:03:41,680
<i>Shoot them!</i>

29
00:03:41,847 --> 00:03:42,848
<i>Shoot her!</i>

30
00:03:43,307 --> 00:03:44,800
What did you do?

31
00:03:45,267 --> 00:03:46,644
What did you do?

32
00:03:46,894 --> 00:03:48,103
<i>Shoot her. Kill her.</i>

33
00:03:48,270 --> 00:03:49,480
<i>Shoot her!</i>

34
00:04:03,369 --> 00:04:05,371
<i>Shoot them all.</i>

35
00:04:06,038 --> 00:04:07,164
<i>Shoot!</i>

36
00:04:13,671 --> 00:04:14,672
<i>Kill!</i>

37
00:04:35,317 --> 00:04:37,278
<i>Kill her. Shoot her.</i>

38
00:04:37,444 --> 00:04:41,156
<i>Kill her. Shoot her.</i>

39
00:04:52,042 --> 00:04:54,253
Honey, you okay? What are you seeing?

40
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,204
Lorraine.

41
00:05:29,705 --> 00:05:31,165
Lorraine, what is happening?

42
00:05:32,082 --> 00:05:33,584
I have to see.

43
00:05:33,751 --> 00:05:35,419
We're through. We're through.
It's time to come back.

44
00:05:40,632 --> 00:05:41,675
What is happening?

45
00:05:46,597 --> 00:05:48,599
It wants to show me.

46
00:07:10,681 --> 00:07:11,682
Lorraine!

47
00:07:12,099 --> 00:07:13,100
Lorraine!

48
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:16,061
Oh, God! Oh!

49
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:17,271
Honey.

50
00:07:17,438 --> 00:07:18,856
Honey.

51
00:07:22,526 --> 00:07:23,694
It's okay.

52
00:07:31,368 --> 00:07:32,578
It's okay.

53
00:07:36,498 --> 00:07:37,499
Ed.

54
00:07:39,710 --> 00:07:42,045
This is as close to hell
as I ever wanna get.

55
00:08:55,661 --> 00:08:56,870
- Damn kids!
- Really.

56
00:08:57,037 --> 00:08:58,080
Yeah.

57
00:09:01,124 --> 00:09:02,125
Oh, my gosh.

58
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:05,671
Keith and I are going to sneak
out tonight with his friend, Michael,

59
00:09:05,837 --> 00:09:07,506
